thread.title: Iraq's April 19 air strike in Syria killed 36 IS militants - spokesman

title: Iraq's April 19 air strike in Syria killed 36 IS militants - spokesman
text:
April 22, 2018 / 11:45 AM / Updated an hour ago Iraq's April 19 air strike in Syria killed 36 IS militants - spokesman Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
BAGHDAD (Reuters) - An Iraqi air strike in Syria on April 19 has killed 36 Islamic State militants, including some of the groupâ€™s leaders in Syria, an Iraqi military spokesman told Reuters on Sunday. 
Iraqi warplanes had attacked an Islamic State explosives factory and other positions inside Syria on Thursday, a rare air assault across the border. Reporting by Ahmed Aboulenein; editing by Maher Chmaytelli
